            <div>
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#01407a] mb-3">Insurance Coverage</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-4">
                Appropriate business insurance including liability and garage keeper coverage.
              </p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-gray-600">
                <li class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                  <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-[#c9a227] flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span>General liability insurance</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                  <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-[#c9a227] flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span>Garage keeper's coverage</span>
                </li>
                <li class="flex items-center space-x-2">
                  <Icon name="tabler:check" class="w-4 h-4 text-[#c9a227] flex-shrink-0" />
                  <span>Professional indemnity</span>
